== 制作 ==
=== 发展 ===
塔伦蒂诺用了超过十年来写本片的剧本，他在一次采访中对[[查理·罗斯|查理·罗斯]]说，他变得“太宝贝每一页了”，这个故事不断地发展扩大<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.allheadlinenews.com/articles/7011717003|title=Quentin Tarantino Spends Decade Writing WWII Drama|work=All Headline News|publisher=AHN Media|first=Jan|last=Westmark|date=2008-07-24|accessdate=2010-01-25|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5nE4PF7W4?url=http://www.allheadlinenews.com/articles/7011717003|archivedate=2010-02-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite video | url = http://www.charlierose.com/view/interview/10567 | people = Quentin Tarantino, Charlie Rose | title = An hour with Filmmaker Quentin Tarantino about his film 'Inglourious Basterds' | time = 10min 38s | publisher = Charlie Rose | format = FLV | date = 2009-08-21 | accessdate = 2010-02-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100304205043/http://www.charlierose.com/view/interview/10567 | archive-date = 2010-03-04 | dead-url = yes }} {{Wayback|url=http://www.charlierose.com/view/interview/10567 |date=20100304205043 }}</ref>。塔伦蒂诺把该剧本视为正在发展中的杰作，他感觉它一定会成为他写过的最好的作品<ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.movieweb.com/movie/FI3s3c65CkCR5c/RELc0RMQ2vHwPM| title = Inglourious Basterds: Review By WiseGuy| work = MovieWeb| publisher = Fandango| date = September 2009| accessdate = 2010-02-01| archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/5nE4Ug611?url=http://www.movieweb.com/movie/FI3s3c65CkCR5c/RELc0RMQ2vHwPM| archivedate = 2010-02-01| dead-url = yes}}</ref>。塔伦蒂诺预想这部电影会是“一帮家伙接下任务”那类影片<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2009/05/10/movies/10hoha.html?_r=2&ref=movies&|title=‘Bunch of Guys on a Mission Movie’|last=Hohenadel|first=Kristin|date=2009-05-06|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|publisher=The New York Times Company|accessdate=2013-02-22|archive-date=2018-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181115203804/https://www.nytimes.com/2009/05/10/movies/10hoha.html?_r=2&ref=movies&|dead-url=no}}</ref>，他说它会是“我自己的《[[十二金剛|十二金剛]]》、《[[血染雪山堡_(电影)|血染雪山堡]]》或《{{link-en|纳瓦隆大炮|The Guns of Navarone (film)}}》之类的东西”<ref>{{cite news | url= http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/5055906/Battleof-the-blockbusters.html | title= Battle of the blockbusters | work= The Daily Telegraph | first= Marc | last= Lee | date= 2009-03-26 | accessdate= 2010-02-28 | location= London | archive-date= 2009-03-30 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20090330183604/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/5055906/Battleof-the-blockbusters.html | dead-url= no }}</ref>。据塔伦蒂诺说，他所有的电影都能让观众对着那些本不该搞笑的东西发笑，但每部电影的幽默都是不同的。<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.gomolo.in/features/article.aspx?ArticleID=202|title= There Is a Sense of Humour In All of My Movies|work= Gomolo|location= [[India|IN]]|date= 2009-10-01|accessdate= 2010-01-26|archiveurl= https://www.webcitation.org/5nE4e87kz?url=http://www.gomolo.in/features/article.aspx?ArticleID=202|archivedate= 2010-02-01|dead-url= yes}}</ref>

{{quote box|width=30%|align=left|quote=“我打算找到一个很像意大利式西部片中西班牙的地方——一个无主之地。有美国士兵、法国农民、法国抵抗势力和德国占领军，它算是无主之地。那真的会是我自己的意大利式西部片，不过是加上二战标签的。但我不会很在意这部电影的特定历史背景。我不会仅仅演奏[[艾迪特·皮雅芙|艾迪特·皮雅芙]]和[[安德鲁斯姐妹|安德鲁斯姐妹]]的音乐。我还可以[[饒舌|说唱]]，我可以无所不能。关键是让内部饱满。”<ref>{{cite journal | url=http://www.allbusiness.com/services/motion-pictures/4885660-1.html | first=Dylan | last=Callaghan | title=Dialogue with Quentin Tarantino | journal=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] | publisher=[[Nielsen_Company|Nielsen]] | date=2003-10-10 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090301144803/http://www.allbusiness.com/services/motion-pictures/4885660-1.html | archivedate=2009-03-01 | author= | access-date=2011-10-16 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>|source=—昆汀·塔伦蒂诺}}

到了2002年，塔伦蒂诺发现《无耻混蛋》的制作规模会比他构想中的大，并看到有其他导演在拍二战题材的电影<ref name=beijing>{{cite news |url= http://www.nytimes.com/2002/09/05/movies/tarantino-behind-the-camera-in-beijing.html?pagewanted=all |title= Tarantino Behind the Camera in Beijing |work= [[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |publisher= The New York Times Company |first= Rick |last= Lyman |date= 2002-09-05 |accessdate= 2010-01-26 |archiveurl= https://www.webcitation.org/5nE4gQg3G?url=http://www.nytimes.com/2002/09/05/movies/tarantino-behind-the-camera-in-beijing.html |archivedate= 2010-02-01 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。那时，他已经写出了三版几乎完成的剧本，宣称它是“我的最佳作品之一，但我无法想出一个结尾”<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.usatoday.com/life/movies/news/2003-10-05-tarantino_x.htm|first=Scott|last=Bowles|title=Tarantino goes for the 'Kill'|work=[[USA_Today|USA Today]]|publisher=[[Gannett_Company|Gannet]]|date=2003-10-06|accessdate=2010-01-26|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5nE4iAeE0?url=http://www.usatoday.com/life/movies/news/2003-10-05-tarantino_x.htm|archivedate=2010-02-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。于是，他将其搁置一边，先导演了两部《[[杀死比尔|杀死比尔]]》（2003-2004年）<ref name = beijing />。完成后，塔伦蒂诺重新审视了他的第一稿故事线，想出把它变成一个迷你系列剧的主意。然而，他修剪了剧本，用《[[低俗小说|低俗小说]]》的剧本来作为长度的参照依据<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.news.com.au/couriermail/story/0,23739,25939754-7642,00.html|title=Tarantino's glorious 'masterpiece'|work=The Courier Mail|first=Rachel|last=Jones|date=2009-08-17|accessdate=2010-02-28|archive-date=2021-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420225941/https://www.couriermail.com.au/?nk=761ee7d389e908ca87f3b0211654b798-1618959581|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然后他计划于2005年开始《无耻混蛋》的制作<ref name="MTV">{{cite web|url= http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1510005/20050920/story.jhtml|title= Tarantino Gushes About 'Grind,' Says Next 'Kill Bill' Is 10 Years Away|work= MTV|first= Larry|last= Carroll|date= 2005-09-20|accessdate= 2010-02-28|archive-date= 2010-02-11|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20100211232618/http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1510005/20050920/story.jhtml|dead-url= no}}</ref>。修改后的版本讲述了一群逃脱死刑的士兵开始一项帮助[[盟军|盟军]]的任务。他描述这些人为“不是你们那种常规的、在二战中陷入了重要事件的英雄类型”<ref>{{cite web| url= http://www.bbc.co.uk/dna/h2g2/A1111447| title= Quentin Tarantino – Film Maker| work= H2G2| publisher= BBC| accessdate= 2010-02-28| archive-date= 2010-11-30| archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20101130180740/http://www.bbc.co.uk/dna/h2g2/A1111447| dead-url= no}}</ref>。

2004年11月，塔伦蒂诺决定暂缓该片的制作，而是去[[三池崇史|三池崇史]]的[[意大利式西部片|意大利式西部片]]《[[日式牛仔一品鍋|日式牛仔一品鍋]]》中出演了一个角色，并想要拍一部完全用[[中文|中文]]的[[功夫|功夫]]片<ref>{{cite news|url= http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2004/nov/02/china.film|title= Tarantino plans old-style kung fu film – in Mandarin|work= The Guardian|publisher= Guardian Media|first= Steve|last= Rose|date= 2004-11-12|accessdate= 2010-01-26|archiveurl= https://www.webcitation.org/5nE4uVnT9?url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2004/nov/02/china.film|archivedate= 2010-02-01|location= London|dead-url= no}}</ref>。这个计划也失败了，最终他导演了《{{link-en|刑房 (电影)|Grindhouse (film)|刑房}}》中的一部，之后回到了本片的制作上来<ref name="MTV"/>。本片片名来自{{link-en|恩佐·卡斯提拉里|Enzo G. Castellari}}1978年导演的战争片《{{link-en|戴罪立功|The Inglorious Bastards}}》的英文片名“{{lang|en|The Inglorious Bastards}}”<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/arts/film/story/2009/08/20/f-inglourious-basterds-review.html |title=Inglourious Basterds Review |publisher=CBC News |accessdate=2010-01-18 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5nE4yfZiA?url=http://www.cbc.ca/arts/film/story/2009/08/20/f-inglourious-basterds-review.html |archivedate=2010-02-01 |date=2009-08-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Inglourious Guide">{{cite news |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2009/aug/15/inglourious-basterds-guide |title=Inglourious Basterds Guide |work=The Guardian |publisher=Guardian Media |accessdate=2010-01-19 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5nE5HOJyN?url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2009/aug/15/inglourious-basterds-guide |archivedate=2010-02-01 |location=London |first=Damon |last=Wise |date=2009-08-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在戛纳电影节的新闻发布会上，塔伦蒂诺被问到对《无耻混蛋》片名拼写的解释，他说：“我永远不会解释这个问题的。<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/32588484 | title = Inglourious Basterds has one tricky title | work = [[MSNBC.com|MSNBC.com]] | agency = [[Associated_Press|Associated Press]] | date = 2009-08-27 | accessdate = 2010-01-18 | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/5nE51FAL0?url=http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/32588484 | archivedate = 2010-02-01 | dead-url = no }}</ref>”被继续逼问后，他虽然没有解释“{{lang|en|Inglourious}}”中多出来的“{{lang|en|u}}”，但他说：“混蛋？这就是你说这个词的正常方式：混蛋。{{efn|原文：{{lang|en|The Basterds? That's just the way you say it: Basterds.}}}}<ref name="Inglourious Guide"/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.empireonline.com/features/tarantino-talks-inglourious-basterds-trailer/ |title=Quentin Tarantino on the Inglourious Basterds Trailer |work=[[Empire_(magazine)|Empire]] |publisher=[[Bauer_Media_Group|Bauer Media]] |date=2009-02-12 |accessdate=2009-08-19 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5nE5PdZRo?url=http://www.empireonline.com/features/tarantino-talks-inglourious-basterds-trailer/default.asp |archivedate=2010-02-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>”塔伦蒂诺在后来的一次采访中表示他拼错片名中的单词“是一种[[尚·米榭·巴斯奇亞|巴斯奇亞]]式的手段”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.forward.com/articles/112638/|title=Glorious Bastard: Tarantino Talks About His Not-A-Holocaust-Movie|date=2009-08-21|work=[[The_Forward|The Forward]]|publisher=Forward Association|accessdate=2009-09-12|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5nE5c9mXV?url=http://ttp//www.forward.com/articles/112638/|archivedate=2010-02-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他在[[晚间秀|晚间秀]]上进一步解释“{{lang|en|Inglourious Basterds}}”是一种“昆汀·塔伦蒂诺式拼法”<ref>{{cite episode |title= Quentin Tarantino Interview|series = Late Show with David Letterman|serieslink=Late Show with David Letterman|credits= Letterman, David and Tarantino, Quentin|network=[[CBS|CBS]]|airdate=August 17, 2009| accessdate=2011-04-27}}</ref>
。

