塔伦蒂诺原想让[[莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥|莱昂纳多·迪卡普里奥]]扮演汉斯·兰达<ref>{{cite news|first=Michael|last=Fleming|url=http://www.variety.com/VR1117988993.html|title=Quentin Tarantino seeks 'Bastards'|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|publisher=Reed Business Information|date=2008-07-15|accessdate=July 29, 2008<!-- |archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/5nE66KNq7|archivedate=February 1, 2010 -->|archive-date=2010-02-01|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5nE66KNq7?url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117988993.html?categoryid=1975|dead-url=no}}</ref>，之后决定应让更年长的德国演员出演<ref name=deck>{{cite news|first=Michael|last=Fleming|author2=Tatiana Siegel|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117990111.html?categoryid=13&cs=1&nid=2564|title=Eli Roth on deck for 'Bastards'|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|publisher=Reed Business Information|date=2008-08-05|accessdate=August 6, 2008<!-- |archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/5nE67JaMk|archivedate= February 1, 2010 -->|archive-date=2009-09-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090902193732/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117990111.html?categoryid=13&cs=1&nid=2564|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该角色最终归于奥地利演员[[克里斯托弗·瓦尔兹|克里斯托弗·瓦尔兹]]，塔伦蒂诺本害怕该角色“无法被演绎”，称瓦尔兹“成就了我的电影”<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118003822?refCatId=3628|title=Tarantino Reflects On 'Basterds'|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|publisher=Reed Business Information|date=2009-05-17|accessdate=December 23, 2011<!-- |archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/5nE6DBVxC|archivedate= February 1, 2010 -->|first=Michael|last=Fleming|archive-date=2010-02-01|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5nE6DBVxC?url=http://ttp//www.variety.com/index.asp?layout=festivals|dead-url=no}}</ref>。皮特和塔伦蒂诺几年来一直想合作，但没有等到合适的影片<ref name="CNNPitt">{{cite news|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2009/SHOWBIZ/Movies/08/19/tarantino.pitt.basterds/index.html|title=Tarantino and Pitt: The long-awaited love affair|work=[[CNN|CNN]]|publisher=[[Time_Warner|Time Warner]]|first=Jim|last=Stenman|date=2009-08-21|accessdate=2010-01-31|archive-date=2010-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100114050801/http://edition.cnn.com/2009/SHOWBIZ/Movies/08/19/tarantino.pitt.basterds/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。当塔伦蒂诺的剧本写到一半时，他感觉皮特可能会很合适艾多·瑞恩这个角色。等他完成剧本后，他认为皮特“会非常棒”，便联系了皮特的经纪人问他是否有时间<ref name="CNNPitt"/>。

塔伦蒂诺让[[亞當·山德勒|亞當·山德勒]]扮演唐尼·唐诺维兹，但山德勒因影片《{{link-en|滑稽人物|Funny People}}》的档期冲突而拒绝邀约<ref name="mtv">{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1619322/story.jhtml|title=Inglourious Basterds Original Cast Plans Called For Leonardo DiCaprio, Adam Sandler|last=Ditzian|first=Eric|work=[[MTV.com|MTV.com]]|publisher=[[Viacom|Viacom]]|date=2009-08-24|accessdate=January 18, 2010<!-- |archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/5nE6GGVMq|archivedate= February 1, 2010 -->|archive-date=2010-02-01|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5nE6GGVMq?url=http://www.mtv.com/movies/news/articles/1619322/story.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[伊萊·羅斯|伊萊·羅斯]]取而代之，他也导演了电影中的电影《国家的荣耀》<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118007314.html?categoryid=13&cs=1&ref=bd_film|title=Film Faux Draws A Double Take|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|publisher=[[Reed_Business_Information|Reed Business Information]]|first=Justin|last=Kroll|date=2009-08-14|accessdate=January 31, 2010 <!-- | archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/5nCbhPGyh | archivedate=January 31, 2010 -->|archive-date=2010-01-31|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5nCbhPGyh?url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118007314.html?categoryid=13&cs=1&ref=bd_film|dead-url=no}}</ref>，用了300位群众演员<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.collider.com/2009/12/15/eli-roth-talks-sci-fi-movie-dangerous-species-and-more/|title=Eli Roth Talks Sci-Fi Movie ENDANGERED SPECIES and More|first=Jonathan|last=Callan|work=Collider.com|date=2009-01-15|accessdate=January 31, 2010 <!-- | archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/5nCbLlnGP | archivedate=January 31, 2010 -->|archive-date=2010-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100522031455/http://www.collider.com/2009/12/15/eli-roth-talks-sci-fi-movie-dangerous-species-and-more/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。导演也原想让[[西蒙·佩吉|西蒙·佩吉]]出演英国影评人阿尔奇·希考克斯，但佩吉因[[斯皮尔伯格|斯皮尔伯格]]的《[[丁丁历险记_(电影)|丁丁历险记]]》的时间安排而被迫退出<ref name=fassbender>{{cite news|first=Ali|last=Jaafar|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117990808.html?categoryid=13&cs=1&nid=2564|title=Fassbender in talks for 'Bastards'|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|publisher=Reed Business Information|date=2008-08-19|accessdate=August 20, 2008<!-- |archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/5nE6JzTFt |archivedate=February 1, 2010 -->|archive-date=2009-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090830213816/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117990808.html?categoryid=13&cs=1&nid=2564|dead-url=no}}</ref>。德裔爱尔兰演员[[迈克尔·法斯宾德|迈克尔·法斯宾德]]于2008年8月加入剧组出演该角色<ref name=fassbender/>。美剧《[[辦公室_(美國電視劇)|辦公室]]》的演员及编剧[[本杰明·诺瓦克|本杰明·诺瓦克]]也在2008年8月加入，饰演一等兵史密森·尤提维奇，“一位纽约出生、体格纤弱的士兵”<ref>{{cite web|last=Sciretta|first=Peter|title=B.J. Novak Cast in Tarantino's Inglorious Basterds|url=http://www.slashfilm.com/bj-novak-cast-in-tarantinos-inglorious-bastards/|work=SlashFilm|publisher=[[惡棍特工/Film|惡棍特工//Film]]|accessdate=2011-01-01|date=2008-08-06|archive-date=2012-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120927070940/http://www.slashfilm.com/bj-novak-cast-in-tarantinos-inglorious-bastards/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

塔伦蒂诺和德国演员[[娜妲莎·金斯基|娜妲莎·金斯基]]谈过让她扮演影星布丽姬特·冯·汉莫斯马克，甚至飞到德国和她见面，但他们没有协商成功<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/film/news/e3i70662f7dd9d6f3c428c389494a8bc280|title=Tarantino gets his French girl|first=Borys|last=Kit|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|publisher=[[Nielsen_Business_Media|Nielsen Business Media]]|date=2008-09-02|accessdate=2010-01-30|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5nE6OOkvc?url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/film/news/e3i70662f7dd9d6f3c428c389494a8bc280|archivedate=2010-02-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而[[黛安·克鲁格|黛安·克鲁格]]最终出演此角色<ref name="mtv"/><ref name=KrugerWaltzJoinTarantino>{{cite news|title=Kruger, Waltz join Tarantino film|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117991354.html?categoryid=13&cs=1|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|publisher=Reed Business Information|date=2008-08-29|accessdate=January 30, 2010<!-- |archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/5nE6SNXDo |archivedate=February 1, 2010 -->|first=Michael|last=Fleming|archive-date=2009-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090923005256/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117991354.html?categoryid=13&cs=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[罗德·泰勒|罗德·泰勒]]本已经从演艺界退休，不再有经纪人，但在塔伦提诺提出让他出演[[温斯顿·丘吉尔|温斯顿·丘吉尔]]后，他重新复出接下角色<ref name=miamih>{{cite news|first=Scott|last=Eyman|title=Tarantino Comes Calling With A Role For Rod Taylor|url=http://www.miamiherald.com/living/story/1196616.html|work=[[The_Miami_Herald|The Miami Herald]]|publisher=[[The_McClatchy_Company|The McClatchy Company]]|date=2009-08-23|accessdate=2009-08-20|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5kJ4OVKYY?url=http://www.miamiherald.com/living/story/1196616.html|archivedate=2009-10-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。泰勒为正确模仿首相的姿态、手势、声音，甚至口齿不清的说法方式，看了许多丘吉尔的影像片段<ref name=miamih/>。泰勒原本在谈话中推荐[[亞伯特·芬尼|亞伯特·芬尼]]出演该角色，但因塔伦蒂诺的“热情”而同意出演<ref name=miamih/> 。[[麦克·迈尔斯|麦克·迈尔斯]]（爱德·费内奇上将饰演者）是塔伦蒂诺的影迷，曾询问是否能出演本片，因为他的父母曾是[[英國軍隊|英國軍人]]<ref>{{cite web | url=http://toronto.ctv.ca/servlet/an/local/CTVNews/20090813/myers_tarantino_090813/20090813?hub=TorontoNewHome | title=Mike Myers a perfect fit for 'Basterds': Tarantino | work=[[The_Canadian_Press|The Canadian Press]] | publisher=[[CTV_News_Channel_(Canada)|CTV News]] | date=2009-08-13 | accessdate=January 31, 2010 <!-- | archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/5nCdoNrri | archivedate=January 31, 2010 --> | archive-date=2012-03-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120310045723/http://toronto.ctv.ca/servlet/an/local/CTVNews/20090813/myers_tarantino_090813/20090813?hub=TorontoNewHome | dead-url=no }}</ref>。他用[[公认发音|公认发音]]作为角色的口音以符合他军官阶层的身份，但态度大致上为“我已经受够了这个战争，如果这位老兄可以结束它，那太好了，因为我的国家已经成了废墟”{{efn|原文：{{lang|en|I'm fed up with this war and if this dude can end it, great because my country is in ruins.}}}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gomolo.in/features/article.aspx?ArticleID=204|title=Mike Myers: I Feel So Honored To Be Able To Do What I Do|publisher=Gomolo.in|date=2010-09-30|accessdate=January 18, 2010 <!-- | archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/5nCdyOzYf | archivedate=January 31, 2010 -->|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5nCdyOzYf?url=http://www.gomolo.in/features/article.aspx?ArticleID=204|archive-date=2010-01-31|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

本片片名灵感来源《{{link-en|戴罪立功|The Inglorious Bastards}}》的导演{{link-en|恩佐·卡斯提拉里|Enzo G. Castellari}}在片中的首映式部分[[友情客串|彩蛋式出境]]。他也在自己1960年的原作中友情客串了一位德国人，在本片中他客串的是军衔和所属组织不同的相同角色<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.festival-cannes.com/assets/Image/Direct/029846.pdf|title=Inglourious Basterds|publisher=Cannes Festival|format=PDF|accessdate=January 18, 2010<!-- |archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/5nE6ey4s6|archivedate=February 1, 2010 -->|archive-date=2010-02-01|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5nE6ey4s6?url=http://www.festival-cannes.com/assets/Image/Direct/029846.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118003930.html?categoryid=13&cs=1|title=Enzo and Tarantino: 'Basterds' brothers|first=Nick|last=Vivarelli|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|publisher=Reed Business Information|date=2009-05-19|accessdate=January 18, 2010<!-- |archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/5nE6jDiZf |archivedate=February 1, 2010 -->|archive-date=2009-08-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090829123400/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118003930.html?categoryid=13&cs=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。主演了《戴罪立功》的{{link-en|博·史文森|Bo Svenson}}也在《国家的荣耀》中友情客串了一位美国上校<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.screendaily.com/5001437.article|first=Mike|last=Goodridge|title=Inglourious Basterds Review|work=Screen Daily|publisher=EMAP Media|date=2010-05-25|accessdate=January 19, 2010<!-- |archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/5nE6oDOwu|archivedate=February 1, 2010 -->|archive-date=2010-02-01|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5nE6oDOwu?url=http://www.screendaily.com/5001437.article|dead-url=no}}</ref>。两位之前主演过塔伦蒂诺电影的演员[[森姆·積遜|森姆·積遜]]和[[哈维·凯特尔|哈维·凯特尔]]在本片中贡献了声音，分别作为旁白和美国[[战略情报局|战略情报局]]指挥官<ref name=jackson-keitel>{{cite web|url=http://popwatch.ew.com/2009/08/19/inglourious-basterds-playing-spot-the-tarantino-reference/|title='Inglourious Basterds':Playing spot the Tarantino reference|last=Nashawaty|first=Chris|date=2009-08-19|work=Entertainment Weekly|accessdate=2010-02-22|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5nk00Mr2E?url=http://popwatch.ew.com/2009/08/19/inglourious-basterds-playing-spot-the-tarantino-reference/|archivedate=2010-02-22|deadurl=no}}</ref>。[[克劳斯·利特曼|克劳斯·利特曼]]和[[張曼玉|張曼玉]]饰演的两个角色的戏份因电影长度原因被最终删除<ref name=leachmanscene>{{cite news|url=http://nymag.com/daily/entertainment/2009/06/cloris_leachman.html|title=Cloris Leachman on Dancing, Inglourious Basterds, and Her Sex Pact With Ed Asner|work=[[New_York_(magazine)|New York]]|publisher=New York Media LLC|first=Jada|last=Yuan|date=2009-06-19|accessdate=2010-02-28|archive-date=2009-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090623063300/http://nymag.com/daily/entertainment/2009/06/cloris_leachman.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://tianjin.chinadaily.com.cn/showbiz/2009-05/22/content_7933941.htm|title=Maggie Cheung Okays with 'Basterds' Cut|work=[[China_Daily|China Daily]]|publisher=People's Republic of China|date=2009-05-22|accessdate=January 21, 2010<!-- |archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/5nE7r2PSx |archivedate=February 1, 2010 -->|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5nE7r2PSx?url=http://tianjin.chinadaily.com.cn/showbiz/2009-05/22/content_7933941.htm|archive-date=2010-02-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref>
。

=== 拍摄 ===
塔伦蒂诺与[[溫斯坦影業|溫斯坦影業]]合作制片<ref>{{cite news | url = http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/film/article1672383.ece | title = Has Tarantino Been Flushed Away? | work = [[The_Times|The Times]] | publisher = [[News_Corporation|News Corp]] | first = Kevin | last = Maher | date = 2007-04-19 | accessdate = 2010-01-26 | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/5nE8195tz?url=http://entertainment.timesonline.co.uk/tol/arts_and_entertainment/film/article1672383.ece | archivedate = 2010-02-01 | location = London | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2008年7月，他和执行制片[[哈維·溫斯坦|哈維]]和{{link-en|鲍勃·韦恩斯坦|Bob_Weinstein}}为使本片赶上2009年的[[戛纳电影节|戛纳电影节]]竞争[[金棕榈奖|金棕榈奖]]而安排了加快的日程计划<ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.mymovies.net/news/news_item.asp?t=Tarantino+Prepping+%22Bastards%22+for+an+October+Start&filmid=1590&nid=5129&s=3&n=| title = Tarantino Prepping "Bastards" for an October Start| publisher = [http://www.mymovies.net/about/about.htm My Movies]| date = 2008-09-07| accessdate = 2010-01-25| archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/5nE8LM5Nq?url=http://www.mymovies.net/news/news_item.asp?t=Tarantino+Prepping+%22Bastards%22+for+an+October+Start| archivedate = 2010-02-01}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url= http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/8014179.stm | title= Tarantino Up For Top Cannes Prize | work= [[BBC_News|News]] | publisher= BBC | date= 2009-04-23 | accessdate= 2010-01-25 | archiveurl= https://www.webcitation.org/5nE8OeJbA?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/8014179.stm | archivedate= 2010-02-01 | dead-url= no }}</ref>。韦恩斯坦影业投资了影片预算的一部分，并成为它在美国的发行商。[[环球影业|环球影业]]与其签订协议，投资了剩余部分，负责美国国外的发行<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2009/06/08/business/media/08weinstein.html|title=Weinstein Company Takes Step to Ease Debt|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|first=Michael|last=Cieply|date=2009-06-07|accessdate=2010-02-28|archive-date=2013-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130513061556/http://www.nytimes.com/2009/06/08/business/media/08weinstein.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=universal>{{cite journal|first=Borys|last=Kit|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/film/news/e3i0e5e7151b1d77beb5d561526c30d032b|title=Universal, Weinstein Co. negotiating 'Bastards'|journal=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|publisher=[[Nielsen_Company|Nielsen]]|date=2008-07-29|accessdate=2008-07-30|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5nE8VAQtY?url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/hr/content_display/film/news/e3i0e5e7151b1d77beb5d561526c30d032b|archivedate=2010-02-01|author=|dead-url=no}}</ref>。德国和法国被选为拍摄地，{{link-en|主要拍摄工作|Principal photography}}于2008年10月在德国的外景地开始<ref>{{cite web | title = Photos & une vidéo du tournage d’" Inglorious basterds " à Paris dans le 18ème | url = http://www.kdbuzz.com/index.php?2008/12/18/251-photos-et-une-video-du-tournage-d-inglourious-basterds-a-paris-dans-le-18eme | trans_title = Photos and a video of the shooting of "Inglourious Basterds" at Paris in the 18ème ''arondissement'' | publisher = KD buzz | language = fr | date = 2008-12-18 | accessdate = 2010-01-19 | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/5nE8XovhY?url=http://www.kdbuzz.com/index.php?2008%2F12%2F18%2F251-photos-et-une-video-du-tournage-d-inglourious-basterds-a-paris-dans-le-18eme | archivedate = 2010-02-01 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name =eyes>{{cite journal | first = Michael | last = Fleming | url = http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117989675.html?categoryid=13&cs=1&nid=2564 | title = Universal eyes Tarantino's 'Bastards' | journal = [[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | publisher = Reed Business Information | date = 2008-07-29 | accessdate = 2008-07-29 | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/5nE8bBTgg?url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117989675.html?categoryid=13 | archivedate = 2010-02-01 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.worstpreviews.com/headline.php?id=10430|title=Quentin Tarantino's "Inglourious Basterds" Began Principal Photography|publisher=WorstPreviews.com|date=2008-10-15|accessdate=2010-01-20|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5nE8jycOu?url=http://www.worstpreviews.com/headline.php?id=10430|archivedate=2010-02-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。拍摄按计划开始于10月13日<ref name = pitt>{{cite journal | first1= Michael | last1= Fleming | first2= Tatiana | last2= Siegel | url= http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117990231.html?categoryid=13&cs=1&nid=2564 | title= Brad Pitt is officially a 'Bastard' | journal= [[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | publisher= Reed Business Information | date= 2008-08-07 | accessdate= 2008-08-07 | archiveurl= https://www.webcitation.org/5nE8qEKtC?url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1117990231.html?categoryid=13 | archivedate= 2010-02-01 }}</ref><ref name=shooting>{{cite news | url = http://movies.ign.com/articles/919/919660p1.html | title = Inglourious Basterds Begins | date = 2008-10-14 | work = [[IGN_Entertainment|IGN Entertainment]] | publisher = News Corp | accessdate = 2008-10-14 | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/5nE8wOcBe?url=http://movies.ign.com/articles/919/919660p1.html | archivedate = 2010-02-01 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。{{link-en|乔治·尼克特洛|Gregory Nicotero}}的工作室（{{lang|en|KNB Efx Group}}）负责特效<ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.knbefxgroup.com/knb_alt2.html| title = Contender Q and A With Greg Nicotero| publisher = KNB EFX| date = 2009-12-12| accessdate = 2010-02-01| archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/5nE925fbz?url=http://www.knbefxgroup.com/knb_alt2.html| archivedate = 2010-02-01| dead-url = yes}}</ref>。大部分影片在德国[[波茨坦|波茨坦]]的[[巴貝爾堡攝影棚|巴貝爾堡攝影棚]]<ref name=Kulish>{{cite news | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2009/02/16/world/europe/16germany.html | first = Nicholas | last = Kulish | title = Winslet and Cruise Star in a German Studio's Latest Act | work = [[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] | date = 2009-02-15 | accessdate = 2010-01-20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20171230115358/http://www.nytimes.com/2009/02/16/world/europe/16germany.html | archivedate = 2017-12-30 | dead-url = no }}</ref>和德国捷克边境的{{link-en|温泉小镇|Spa_town}}[[巴德尚道|巴德尚道]]完成拍摄和剪辑<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.atnzone.com/nz/2009/08/27/movie-review-inglourious-basterds | title = Movie Review: Inglourious Basterds | publisher = ATN zone | date = 2009-08-27 | accessdate = 2010-01-20 | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/5nE9FMHSy?url=http://ttp//www.atnzone.com/nz/2009/08/27/movie-review-inglourious-basterds | archivedate = 2010-02-01 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。罗斯说他们在影院着火那场戏中“几乎被焚烧了”，原先安排的火焰温度为400℃（750℉），但实际温度为1200℃（2000℉）。他还声称影院的纳粹标志也不该倒下来，因为它是用钢缆固定的，但钢在火中变软折断了<ref name="roth survives">{{cite news|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2009/aug/16/entertainment/ca-roth16|title=Eli Roth barely survives acting in Quentin Tarantino's 'Inglourious Basterds'|last=Lee|first=Chris|date=2009-08-16|work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|publisher=Tribune Company|accessdate=2010-02-05|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5nIyLndwa?url=http://articles.latimes.com/2009/aug/16/entertainment/ca-roth16|archivedate=2010-02-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年1月11日，在[[BBC|BBC]]电台的节目“[[格莱汉姆·诺顿秀|格莱汉姆·诺顿秀]]”上 ，塔伦蒂诺说在克鲁格被勒死的那场戏中，他自己用手勒了她，只拍了一遍就完成，为了增加真实度<ref>{{Citation | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b006xnzc | volume = Series 12 | number = Episode 11 | contribution = Graham Norton Show | title = BBC1 | type = broadcast | date = 2013-01-11 | accessdate = 2014-06-07 | archive-date = 2014-05-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140528203812/http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b006xnzc | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

影片在戛纳上映后，塔伦蒂诺表示他会在院线公映前的六月重新剪辑本片，让他有时间加入一些赶不及戛纳首映的场景<ref>{{cite journal | url=http://weblogs.variety.com/thompsononhollywood/2009/05/tarantino-update.html | title=Thompson on Hollywood – Tarantino Update | last=Thompson | first=Anne | date=2009-05-25 | work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | publisher=Reed Business Information | accessdate=2009-05-26 | archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5nE9SKX5Z?url=http://weblogs.variety.com/thompsononhollywood/2009/05/tarantino-update.html | archivedate=2010-02-01 | journal= }}</ref>。

=== 配乐 ===
塔伦蒂诺原想让[[恩尼奥·莫里科内|恩尼奥·莫里科内]]为本片创作配乐<ref name = "Inglourious Guide" />，但莫里科内无法参与，因为和他为[[朱賽貝·托納多雷|朱賽貝·托納多雷]]的影片《{{link-en|巴阿里亚|Baarìa (film)}}》的配乐工作在时间上有冲突<ref>{{cite web|url= http://www.joblo.com/index.php?id=morricone-u-basterd|title= Morricone u Basterd!|work= JoBlo.com|accessdate= 2009-09-26|archiveurl= https://www.webcitation.org/5nFji5kJj?url=http://www.joblo.com/index.php?id=morricone-u-basterd|archivedate= 2010-02-02|dead-url= yes}}</ref>。然而，塔伦蒂诺在片中仍然用了8首莫里科内创作的音乐，其中4首被收录进原声带CD中<ref name="WalesOnlineTarantino" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.slantmagazine.com/music/review/inglourious-basterds-original-soundtrack/1822|work=[[Slant_Magazine|Slant Magazine]]|title=Inglourious Basterds Original Soundtrack Review|first=Jesse|last=Cataldo|date=2009-08-31|accessdate=2009-11-23|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5nFjv6uOi?url=http://www.slantmagazine.com/music/review/inglourious-basterds-original-soundtrack/1822|archivedate=2010-02-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

本片的开场主题旋律是取自伪[[民谣|民谣]][[谣曲|谣曲]]《夏日绿叶》（{{lang|en|The Green Leaves of Summer}}），该曲是[[迪米特里·迪奥姆金|迪米特里·迪奥姆金]]和{{link-en|保罗·弗朗克西斯·维布斯特|Paul Francis Webster}}为1960年的影片《{{link-en|边城英烈传|The Alamo (1960 film)}}》的开场所作<ref name="WalesOnlineTarantino">{{cite news|url= http://www.walesonline.co.uk/showbiz-and-lifestyle/film-in-wales/2009/08/23/quentin-tarantino-on-his-ww11-epic-inglourious-basterds-91466-24510448/|title= Quentin Tarantino on his WW2 epic Inglourious Basterds|work= Wales Online|date= 2009-08-23|accessdate= 2010-01-26|archiveurl= https://www.webcitation.org/5nFjSt9Oz?url=http://www.walesonline.co.uk/showbiz-and-lifestyle/film-in-wales/2009/08/23/quentin-tarantino-on-his-ww11-epic-inglourious-basterds-91466-24510448/|archivedate= 2010-02-02|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url= http://hamptonroads.com/2009/08/inglourious-basterds-great-fun-fans-war-movies|title= 'Inglourious Basterds' is great fun for fans of war movies|publisher= Hampton Roads|first= Mal|last= Vincent|date= 2009-08-22|accessdate= 2010-01-26|archiveurl= https://www.webcitation.org/5nFjNCxFr?url=http://hamptonroads.com/2009/08/inglourious-basterds-great-fun-fans-war-movies|archivedate= 2010-02-02|dead-url= no}}</ref>。本片配乐中用到了多种音乐类型，包括[[意大利式西部片|意大利式西部片]]音乐、[[节奏布鲁斯|节奏布鲁斯]]和[[大卫·鲍伊|大卫·鲍伊]]在1982年电影《{{link-en|豹人 (1982年电影)|Cat People (1982 film)|豹人}}》中的同名主题曲<ref>{{cite news | url = http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/music_blog/2009/08/inglourious-basterds-quentin-tarantino.html | title = Quentin Tarantino's method behind 'Inglourious Basterds' soundtrack mix-tape | work = The [[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]] | publisher = Tribune Co | first = Mark | last = Milian | date = 2009-08-22 | accessdate = 2009-02-01 | archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/5nFjXt1kN?url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/music_blog/2009/08/inglourious-basterds-quentin-tarantino.html | archivedate = 2010-02-02 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。这是第一张其中不包含片中部分对话的塔伦蒂诺作品原声带<ref>{{cite web|url=http://music.barnesandnoble.com/Quentin-Tarantinos-Inglourious-Basterds/e/093624974444|title=Quentin Tarantino's Inglourious Basterds CD|work=Barnes & Noble|publisher=All Media Guide|accessdate=2010-02-01|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5nFjbjwZV?url=http://music.barnesandnoble.com/Quentin-Tarantinos-Inglourious-Basterds/e/093624974444|archivedate=2010-02-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，发行于2009年8月18日<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.inglouriousbasterdsmusic.com/ |title = Inglourious Basterds Motion Picture Soundtrack |publisher = Inglourious basterds music |accessdate = 2010-01-24 |archive-date = 2009-07-22 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090722134137/http://www.inglouriousbasterdsmusic.com/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

