劇本的最終版完成后，被泄露到網路上，几个塔伦蒂诺的影迷網站开始发布评论和剧本节选<ref name="firstshowing.net">{{cite web |url=http://www.firstshowing.net/2008/07/10/script-for-quentin-tarantinos-inglorious-bastards-surfaces |title=Script For Tarantino's Inglourious Basterds Surfaces |publisher=First showing |date=2008-07-10 |accessdate=2010-01-18 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5nE9oB3v1?url=http://www.firstshowing.net/2008/07/10/script-for-quentin-tarantinos-inglorious-bastards-surfaces/ |archivedate=2010-02-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url = http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2008/aug/15/quentintarantino.secondworldwar| title = Tarantino's Nazi 'Reservoir Dogs of War' Leaked Online| work = [[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]| publisher = [[Guardian_Media_Group|Guardian Media]]| date = 2008-08-15| accessdate = 2010-01-19| archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/5nE9rdwSc?url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2008/aug/15/quentintarantino.secondworldwar| archivedate = 2010-02-01| location = London| first = Kate| last = Connolly| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

影片完整的先行预告片（{{lang|en|teaser trailer}}）于2009年2月10日在《{{link-en|今夜娱乐 (电视)|Entertainment Tonight|今夜娱乐}}》节目中首发<ref>{{cite journal| url= http://nymag.com/daily/entertainment/2009/02/inglorious_basterds.html| title= Your First Look at Inglourious Basterds| journal= [[New_York_(magazine)|New York]]| publisher= New York Media| date= 2009-02-10| accessdate= 2010-01-18| archiveurl= https://www.webcitation.org/5nE9zXTiz?url=http://nymag.com/daily/entertainment/2009/02/inglorious_basterds.html| archivedate= 2010-02-01| author= | dead-url= no}}</ref>，并于接下来的一周在影院附着影片《[[黑色星期五_(2009年电影)|黑色星期五]]》播放<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cinemablend.com/new/Inglourious-Basterds-Trailer-Coming-This-Week-11933.html|title=Inglourious Basterds Trailer Coming This Week|first=Katey|last=Rich|publisher=Cinema Blend|date=2009-02-09|accessdate=January 21, 2010<!--|archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/5nEA4vNWO |archivedate=February 1, 2010-->|archive-date=2010-02-01|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5nEA4vNWO?url=http://www.cinemablend.com/new/Inglourious-Basterds-Trailer-Coming-This-Week-11933.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该预告片中主要展示了艾多·瑞恩对惡棍-{}-特工的训话，告诉他们伏击、杀害、折磨并割下纳粹士兵头皮的计划，以及一些其他场景<ref name="empiretrailer">{{cite journal|url=http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=24191|title=Inglourious Basterds Trailer Now Online|work=[[Empire_(magazine)|Empire]]|publisher=Bauer Media Group|accessdate=January 20, 2010<!--|archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/5nEAHk8HV|archivedate=February 1, 2010-->|journal=|archive-date=2010-02-01|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5nEAHk8HV?url=http://www.empireonline.com/news/story.asp?NID=24191|dead-url=no}}</ref>。它也突出了意大利式西部片语句“从前在纳粹占领的法国”（{{lang|en|Once Upon A Time In Nazi Occupied France}}）<ref name="empiretrailer"/>，把它作为电影的片名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.kpbs.org/news/2009/aug/21/inglourious-basterds/|title=Cinema Junkie: Inglourious Basterds|work=KPBS|publisher=[[San_Diego_State_University|San Diego State University]]|date=2009-08-21|accessdate=January 20, 2010<!--|archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/5nEAMq9jd|archivedate=February 1, 2010-->|archive-date=2010-02-01|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5nEAMq9jd?url=http://www.kpbs.org/news/2009/aug/21/inglourious-basterds/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，还有“一个混蛋的工作永不会完成”（{{lang|en|A Basterd's Work Is Never Done}}）这句没有出现在正片里的台词（这句话出现在剧本中犹太熊的背景故事里）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://thefilmstage.com/2010/03/02/once-upon-a-time-in-nazi-occupied-france-the-basterds-screenplay/|title=Once Upon a Time In Nazi-Occupied France: The 'Basterds' Screenplay|publisher=The Film Stage|date=2010-03-02|accessdate=March 22, 2010<!--|archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/5oQcd4MMI|archivedate=March 22, 2010-->|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100310080934/http://thefilmstage.com/2010/03/02/once-upon-a-time-in-nazi-occupied-france-the-basterds-screenplay/|archive-date=2010-03-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

本片于2009年8月19日在英国和法国上映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.film.com/features/story/inglourious-basterds-uk-review/29694785|title=Inglourious Basterds UK Review|work=Film|publisher=RealNetworks|first=Lisa|last=Keddie|date=2009-08-14|accessdate=2010-02-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100310053826/http://www.film.com/features/story/inglourious-basterds-uk-review/29694785|archive-date=2010-03-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，比美国的上映日期早两天<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.empireonline.com/News/story.asp?NID=23938 |title= Inglourious Basterds Gets a Release Date |work= Empire |publisher= Bauer Media |accessdate= 2010-01-20 |archiveurl= https://www.webcitation.org/5nEAVfVBX?url=http://www.empireonline.com/News/story.asp?NID=23938 |archivedate= 2010-02-01 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。它于8月20日在德国上映<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.monstersandcritics.com/movies/features/article_1492807.php/In_Pictures_Berlin_Premiere_of_Inglourious_Basterds |title = In Pictures: Berlin Première of Inglourious Basterds |work = Monsters & Critics |publisher = WOTR |accessdate = 2010-02-01 |archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/5nEAcACrw?url=http://www.monstersandcritics.com/movies/features/article_1492807.php/In_Pictures_Berlin_Premiere_of_Inglourious_Basterds |archivedate = 2010-02-01 |dead-url = yes }}</ref>。然而，一些欧洲影院从8月15日起就举行了一些预映会<ref>{{cite news | url= http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/filmblog/2009/aug/25/inglourious-basterds-box-office-previews | title= Inglourious Basterds Box Office Previews | work= The Guardian | publisher= Bauer Media | first= Charles | last= Gant | date= 2009-08-25 | accessdate= 2010-01-22 | archiveurl= https://www.webcitation.org/5nEAebbDH?url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/filmblog/2009/aug/25/inglourious-basterds-box-office-previews | archivedate= 2010-02-01 | location= London | dead-url= no }}</ref>。在波兰，片名没有按原意翻译，被译为《{{lang|pl|Bękarty Wojny}}》（战争的混蛋），从而让纳粹标志卐得以被设计在字母“{{lang|en|O}}”内，影片的其他部分没有遭到改动<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bloblo.pl/image/68941/default/Bekarty+wojny.jpg|title=Polish Inglourious Basterds Poster|work=Chomik|accessdate=2010-02-09|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5ntOoYbw9?url=http://www.bloblo.pl/image/68941/default/Bekarty+wojny.jpg|archivedate=2010-03-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

=== 审查 ===
由于[[德国刑法第86条第一款|德国法律限制纳粹标志的展示]]，[[环球影业|环球影业]]检查了本片的德国宣传网站。片名上的卐被移除，[[德式鋼盔|德式鋼盔]]上的纳粹标志被一个弹孔所替代<ref>{{cite web|author=Universal Studios|title=Nazi Symbols removed from German Movie Site|url=http://movies.universal-pictures-international-germany.de/inglouriousbasterds/|date=2009-07-29|accessdate=2009-07-29|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5ntOUWdez?url=http://movies.universal-pictures-international-germany.de/inglouriousbasterds/|archivedate=2010-03-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。展示纳粹标志的海报在德国网站上无法被下载<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.jwire.com.au/gossip/a-non-jewish-german-journalists-take-oninglourious-basterds/|title=A non-Jewish German journalist's take on "Inglourious Basterds"|last=Bierach|first=Barbara|date=2009-09-13|publisher=Jwire.com|accessdate=September 26, 2009<!--|archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/5ntOeBgnM | archivedate=February 28, 2010-->|archive-date=2010-03-01|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5ntOeBgnM?url=http://www.jwire.com.au/gossip/a-non-jewish-german-journalists-take-oninglourious-basterds/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。尽管广告海报和墙纸不能展示纳粹标志，但根据德国法律这一规定不适用于艺术作品，因此电影本身不会在德国遭到限制<ref>{{cite web|url=http://arstechnica.com/old/content/2007/12/german-politician-sues-unsues-wikipedia-over-nazi-symbols.ars|title=German politician sues, unsues Wikipedia over Nazi symbols|last=Anderson|first=Nate|date=2007-12-07|work=[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]]|publisher=[[Condé_Nast_Publications|Condé Nast Publications]]|accessdate=September 26, 2009<!--|archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/5ntOgwhNP | archivedate=February 28, 2010-->|archive-date=2011-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110606141742/http://arstechnica.com/old/content/2007/12/german-politician-sues-unsues-wikipedia-over-nazi-symbols.ars|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 家庭媒体 ===
本片于2009年12月15日在美国<ref>{{cite web|url=http://backseatcuddler.com/2009/10/20/inglourious-basterds-gets-a-blu-raydvd-release-date/|title='Inglourious Basterds' Gets a Blu-Ray/DVD Release Date|publisher=Backseat cuddler|accessdate=2010-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100125120948/http://backseatcuddler.com/2009/10/20/inglourious-basterds-gets-a-blu-raydvd-release-date/|archive-date=2010-01-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref>和澳大利亚<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ezydvd.com.au/item.zml/809530|title=Inglourious Basterds 2009 DVD|publisher=Ezy DVD|accessdate=2010-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100131064017/http://www.ezydvd.com.au/item.zml/809530|archive-date=2010-01-31|dead-url=yes}}</ref>发行了单碟DVD版、双碟DVD特别版和[[藍光光碟|蓝光]]版，由{{link-en|环球影业家庭娱乐部|Universal Studios Home Entertainment}}出品。它于同年12月15日在英国发行了DVD和蓝光版碟片<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.whsmithentertainment.co.uk/dvd/inglourious-basterds-inglorious-bastards/10064866.html|title=Inglourious Basterds DVD|publisher=W H Smith|accessdate=2010-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100121031456/http://www.whsmithentertainment.co.uk/dvd/inglourious-basterds-inglorious-bastards/10064866.html|archive-date=2010-01-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。在发行后的首周，本片的销售量位于第二，仅次于《[[醉後大丈夫|醉後大丈夫]]》，在美国售出价值为28,467,652美元的1,581,220张碟片<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.the-numbers.com/dvd/charts/weekly/2009/20091220.php|title=US DVD Sales Chart for Week Ending Dec 20, 2009|publisher=Nash Information Services|work=The Numbers|date=2009-12-20|accessdate=2010-02-26|archive-date=2010-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100119161809/http://www.the-numbers.com/dvd/charts/weekly/2009/20091220.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

德国版比美国版长了50秒，因为小酒馆的场景被加长了。尽管该加长场景在其他国家被收录于花絮中，但只有德国院线版、DVD版和蓝光版是将其包含在正片内的。<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.movie-censorship.com/report.php?ID=4237485 |title= Inglorious Basterds |last= Lowrey |first= Michael ‘Mike’ |date= 2010-01-17 |publisher= Movie Censorship |accessdate= 2012-12-05 |archive-date= 2013-02-19 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20130219095743/http://www.movie-censorship.com/report.php?ID=4237485 |dead-url= no }}</ref>

== 反响 ==
=== 票房 ===
本片开映银幕有3165张，在北美的首个周五赚得1430万美元<ref>{{cite web|author=Nicole Sperling|title=Inglourious Basterds gives Quentin Tarantino a box office win on Friday|url=http://hollywoodinsider.ew.com/2009/08/22/inglourious-basterds-gives-quentin-tarantino-a-box-office-win-on-friday/|work=Entertainment Weekly|date=2009-08-04|accessdate=August 22, 2009<!-- |archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/5nFi6pHlB|archivedate=February 2, 2010 -->|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090825081949/http://hollywoodinsider.ew.com/2009/08/22/inglourious-basterds-gives-quentin-tarantino-a-box-office-win-on-friday/|archive-date=2009-08-25|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，到首个周末的票房为3800万美元，创下塔伦蒂诺的个人最佳纪录，并超越《[[第九区|第九区]]》登上票房榜榜首<ref>{{cite web|author=Nicole Sperling|title=Inglourious Basterds rules the weekend box office|url=http://hollywoodinsider.ew.com/2009/08/23/basterds-wins-box-office/|work=Entertainment Weekly|publisher=[[Time_Warner|Time Warner]]|date=2009-08-23|accessdate=September 4, 2009<!-- |archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/5nFiCIycJ |archivedate=February 2, 2010 -->|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090827032237/http://hollywoodinsider.ew.com/2009/08/23/basterds-wins-box-office/|archive-date=2009-08-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。本片在第二个周末退居第二，让位给《[[絕命終結站4|絕命終結站4]]》。第二个周末的票房成绩为2000万美元，在上映后10天内的票房为7380万美元<ref>{{cite web|title='Final Destination' slays 'Inglourious Basterds' at the box office|url=http://www.ticketnews.com/Final-Destination-slays-Inglourious-Basterds-at-the-box-office8093181|work=|publisher=Ticket News|date=2009-08-31|accessdate=September 4, 2009<!-- |archiveurl=http://www.webcitation.org/5nFiJN2XA|archivedate= February 2, 2010 -->|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090904042458/http://www.ticketnews.com/Final-Destination-slays-Inglourious-Basterds-at-the-box-office8093181|archive-date=2009-09-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。《无耻混蛋》以榜首身份在美国国外的22个市场的2650张银幕上开映，收入2749万美元。本片榜首开映的市场包括法国，在500张银幕上收入609万美元。英国市场表现紧随其后，在444张银幕上收入了592万美元（380万英镑）。德国市场为439张银幕和420万美元，澳大利亚市场为266张银幕和256万美元（280万澳元）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.the-numbers.com/interactive/newsStory.php?newsID=4453|title=International Top Five – Glourious Debut for Basterds|date=2009-08-26|work=[http://www.the-numbers.com/about.php The-Numbers]|publisher=Nash Information Services|accessdate=2010-02-25|archive-date=2009-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090831135910/http://www.the-numbers.com/interactive/newsStory.php?newsID=4453|dead-url=no}}</ref>。它在美国和加拿大的票房净收入为1.205亿美元，其他国家的票房总和为2.009亿美元，全球总票房为3.214亿美元。《无耻混蛋》是当时塔伦蒂诺本土和全球票房都为最高的电影，直到被2012年的《[[被解放的姜戈|被解放的姜戈]]》超越<ref>{{cite web|author=Brandon Gray|title=Weekend Report: Moviegoers Feast on 'Meatballs,' Slim Pickings for 'Jennifer'|url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=2615&p=.htm|publisher=[[IMDb|IMDb]]|work=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]]|date=2009-09-21|accessdate=2009-09-27|archive-date=2009-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090924232916/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=2615&p=.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 評價 ===
影评网站[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]显示，273位影评人中的89%给予了本片正面评价，平均分为7.7/10<ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/inglourious_basterds/| title = Inglourious Basterds (2009)| work = [[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]| publisher = Flixster| accessdate = 2012-07-19| archive-date = 2010-02-11| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20100211003630/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/inglourious_basterds/| dead-url = no}}</ref>。该站的总体评价为“一段经典塔伦蒂诺式混合类型的刺激旅程，《无耻混蛋》是暴力的、放纵的，极具娱乐性。<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/inglourious_basterds/?critic=creamcrop | title = Inglourious Basterds RT | work = [[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] | publisher = Flixster | accessdate = 2012-07-19 | archive-date = 2012-04-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120419210215/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/inglourious_basterds/?critic=creamcrop | dead-url = no }}</ref>”百分制影评网站{{lang|en|[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]}}的36篇评论给了本片69分的平均分<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.metacritic.com/film/titles/inglouriousbasterds | title = Inglourious Basterds Reviews | publisher = [[CNET_Networks|CNET Networks]] | work = [[Metacritic|Metacritic]] | accessdate = 2009-09-30 | archive-date = 2009-08-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090816191606/http://www.metacritic.com/film/titles/inglouriousbasterds | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

